Description: monitoring agent for Nagios and compatible systems
 NSClient++ (nscp) is a monitoring agent for Nagios, Naemon, Icinga and
 other compatible monitoring systems. It runs checks locally and exposes
 them over several protocols (NRPE, NSCA, check_mk, ...), and can also
 actively submit results to a central monitoring server.
 .
 This is a minimal, agent-only Linux build: the web frontend and the
 bundled documentation are not included.
